# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFICATION OVERVIEW
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Purpose

The Clinerules Agents specification defines:
- **Agent Rule Packs**: Domain-specific .clinerules configurations
- **Swarm Architecture**: Multi-agent coordination patterns
- **Regulatory Alignment**: Agent behavior compliance with AI regulations
- **Validation Framework**: Agent behavior verification methods

## Key Documents

| Document | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `clinerules-agents-spec.tex` | Main specification document |
| `chapters/01-overview.tex` | Executive overview |
| `chapters/03-agent-rule-pack-architecture.tex` | Rule pack structure |
| `chapters/04-regulatory-agents.tex` | Regulatory compliance agents |
| `chapters/05-swarm-delivery.tex` | Swarm coordination patterns |
| `chapters/06-validation.tex` | Validation and testing |

